  "text": "To indirectly quantify cell plasma membrane damage or rupture, and thus evaluate cytotoxicity of GO and rGO, the lactate dehydrogenase (LDH) assay test (Sigma Aldrich, Belgium) was used at 9 DIVs. Cell viability was calculated (Figure 2f ) as reported in literature [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
